```python
df_sorted = df.sort_values(['batch','hour'])
df_feat = df_sorted.groupby('batch').agg(
    glc_last=('glc','last'),
    lac_max=('lac','max'),
    vc_mean=('viable_cell','mean')
).reset_index()
display(df_feat)
import numpy as np
df_feat['is_unhealthy_batch']=df_feat['vc_mean']<7.0
display(df_feat)
df_feat['pred_unhealthy'] = (df_feat['lac_max']>1.8) | (df_feat['glc_last']<3.8)
display(df_feat)
TP = (df_feat['is_unhealthy_batch']) & (df_feat['pred_unhealthy'])
FP = (~df_feat['is_unhealthy_batch']) & (df_feat['pred_unhealthy'])
TN = (~df_feat['is_unhealthy_batch']) & (~df_feat['pred_unhealthy'])
FN = (df_feat['is_unhealthy_batch']) & (~df_feat['pred_unhealthy'])
display(TP, FP, TN, FN)
```

```python
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
color = np.where(df_feat['is_unhealthy_batch']==True, 'red', 'gray')
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(7,4))
ax.scatter(df_feat['lac_max'],df_feat['vc_mean'], marker ='o', color = color)
ax.set_title("Lactate vs Viable Cell (Batch Health)")
ax.set_xlabel('lac_max')
ax.set_ylabel('vc_mean')
ax.grid(False)
ax.axhline(7, linestyle='--', color='gray', linewidth=2)
```
